content: @@RandomNPC001 Stop spreading fake news. Its was founded by Itau (private bank) and other private companies. Rio's government only secured the public routes and this brought A LOT of tourism to the city, which equals money for the state. Oh, and also, even if it was public money (which it wasnt), that's not how a city budget works, you can't take, for example, spending from education for health and vice verse. Enfim, vai espalhar mentiras em outro lugar, gado.
